OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cold but bright start to the
OL,6,Fday, with sunny spells. Becoming
OL,7,Fincreasingly cloudy into the afternoon
OL,8,Fwith an outside chance of an isolated
OL,9,Fshower. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry evening with some late
OL,12,Fevening sunny spells. Turning cloudier
OL,13,Ffor a time overnight, but likely
OL,14,Fbreaking by dawn. Becoming breezy and
OL,15,Fchilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
