OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FA dry and sunny day with a
OL,6,Flittle patchy cloud, mainly in the
OL,7,Fmorning. Becoming increasingly breezy,
OL,8,Fparticularly over hills. Cloud will
OL,9,Flikely increase overnight from the
OL,10,Feast.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FDry
OL,13,Fwith variable amounts of cloud
OL,14,FWednesday to Friday, though
OL,15,Fincreasingly sunny each afternoon as
OL,16,Fcloud burns back to coasts. Breezy,
OL,17,Fparticularly over hills. Warm, though
OL,18,Fnoticeably cooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
